Roll No: MT25056
Graduate Systems (CSE638) - PA02
Analysis of Network I/O Primitives using perf


==================================================
1. Overview
==================================================

This project implements and analyzes three socket communication models:

A1: Two-Copy using send()/recv()
A2: One-Copy using sendmsg() with scatter-gather
A3: Zero-Copy using sendmsg() with MSG_ZEROCOPY

The programs are implemented using multithreaded TCP client-server architecture
and are profiled using the Linux perf tool.


==================================================
2. Folder Contents
==================================================

Source Files:
- MT25056_Part_A1_Server.c
- MT25056_Part_A1_Client.c
- MT25056_Part_A2_Server.c
- MT25056_Part_A2_Client.c
- MT25056_Part_A3_Server.c
- MT25056_Part_A3_Client.c

Scripts:
- MT25056_Part_C_RunExperiments.sh
- MT25056_Part_D_Plots.py

Build Files:
- Makefile
- README

Data:
- MT25056_Part_C_Results.csv

Report:
- MT25056_Report.pdf


==================================================
3. System Configuration
==================================================

OS: Ubuntu Linux (Dual Boot)
Kernel: 6.8.0-94-generic
CPU: x86_64
Profiler: perf (linux-tools)


==================================================
4. Compilation
==================================================

To compile all programs:

    make

To clean binaries:

    make clean


==================================================
5. Execution Instructions
==================================================

---------------- A1 ----------------

Server:

    ./server_a1 <port> <msg_size>

Client:

    ./client_a1 <server_ip> <port> <msg_size> <threads>


---------------- A2 ----------------

Server:

    ./server_a2 <port> <msg_size>

Client:

    ./client_a2 <server_ip> <port> <msg_size> <threads>


---------------- A3 ----------------

Server:

    ./server_a3 <port> <msg_size>

Client:

    ./client_a3 <server_ip> <port> <msg_size> <threads>


Example:

    ./server_a1 8080 1024
    ./client_a1 127.0.0.1 8080 1024 4


==================================================
6. Part C Automation
==================================================

To run automated experiments:

    ./MT25056_Part_C_RunExperiments.sh

This generates:

    MT25056_Part_C_Results.csv


==================================================
7. Part D Plot Generation
==================================================

To generate plots:

    python3 MT25056_Part_D_Plots.py

This generates PNG files for report screenshots.


